-- Kenya to Allow Use of Retirement Funds as Mortgage Collateral, Kibaki Says
-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 2010-11-10T12:03:38Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-11-10/kenya-to-allow-use-of-retirement-funds-as-mortgage-collateral-kibaki-says.html
Kenya will allow individuals to use
60 percent of their retirement benefits as collateral to secure
mortgages, President Mwai Kibaki said in an e-mailed statement
today.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  